1
00:00:58,560 --> 00:00:59,080
Luo Xin.

2
00:01:00,040 --> 00:01:00,840
Young Master.

3
00:01:04,640 --> 00:01:05,840
Thank you for the ice cream.

4
00:01:05,840 --> 00:01:07,040
I really want to eat it.

5
00:01:07,040 --> 00:01:08,600
But I've been allergic to honey since I was little.

6
00:01:08,600 --> 00:01:09,800
I guess I don't have the luck to enjoy it today.

7
00:01:09,800 --> 00:01:10,800
Sorry about that.

8
00:01:12,120 --> 00:01:12,560
Haoran.

9
00:01:12,560 --> 00:01:13,320
Eat this first,

10
00:01:13,320 --> 00:01:14,120
or it'll melt.

11
00:01:23,120 --> 00:01:23,850
Big brother.

12
00:01:24,560 --> 00:01:27,160
I've been allergic to honey since I was little.

13
00:01:27,800 --> 00:01:28,660
Did you forget?

14
00:01:33,280 --> 00:01:33,840
No, no.

15
00:01:34,720 --> 00:01:35,580
I can't do this.

16
00:01:38,320 --> 00:01:38,840
Luo Xin.

17
00:01:39,800 --> 00:01:40,600
Young Master.

18
00:01:43,039 --> 00:01:43,570
Brother.

19
00:01:44,440 --> 00:01:45,680
Thank you for the ice cream.

20
00:01:45,680 --> 00:01:46,720
I really want to eat it,

21
00:01:46,720 --> 00:01:48,120
but I've been allergic to honey since I was little.

22
00:01:48,120 --> 00:01:49,320
I'm out of luck today.

23
00:01:49,440 --> 00:01:50,039
I'm sorry.

24
00:01:58,920 --> 00:02:00,960
It's fine if you don't eat the ice cream.

25
00:02:00,960 --> 00:02:03,220
I have many other ways to verify it later.

26
00:02:06,040 --> 00:02:07,840
If you had eaten the ice cream just now,

27
00:02:07,840 --> 00:02:08,880
the fact that you're an impostor

28
00:02:08,880 --> 00:02:09,720
would be completely exposed.

29
00:02:09,720 --> 00:02:11,580
That kid is obviously testing us.

30
00:02:11,920 --> 00:02:13,250
Does he know something?

31
00:02:15,360 --> 00:02:15,840
Wait.

32
00:02:17,400 --> 00:02:19,329
Did you guys leak the information?

33
00:02:20,760 --> 00:02:21,560
Probably not.

34
00:02:22,480 --> 00:02:24,360
But you must guard against Gu Haotian.

35
00:02:24,360 --> 00:02:27,090
He always wants to take the young master's place.

36
00:02:27,920 --> 00:02:28,480
Got it.

37
00:02:32,720 --> 00:02:33,980
At 6:00 p.m. tomorrow.

38
00:02:34,160 --> 00:02:36,640
You need to attend the business dinner with the chairman.

39
00:02:36,640 --> 00:02:39,240
This is the information on tomorrow's guests.

40
00:02:39,920 --> 00:02:42,180
You need to memorize each of their names,

41
00:02:42,320 --> 00:02:42,880
faces,

42
00:02:43,480 --> 00:02:45,240
and their companies' information.

43
00:02:45,240 --> 00:02:46,280
They are all Gu Group's

44
00:02:46,280 --> 00:02:47,840
important future partners.

45
00:02:47,840 --> 00:02:49,900
You absolutely cannot drop the ball.

46
00:02:50,840 --> 00:02:51,300
Luo Xin.

47
00:02:51,680 --> 00:02:52,520
Can I decline?

48
00:02:59,040 --> 00:03:00,280
It's just a dinner party.

49
00:03:00,280 --> 00:03:02,010
Isn't a token greeting enough?

50
00:03:10,800 --> 00:03:11,520
Rejected.

51
00:03:24,480 --> 00:03:25,740
You scared me to death.

52
00:03:28,760 --> 00:03:29,760
I'll memorize it.

53
00:03:30,800 --> 00:03:32,060
I... I'll memorize it.

54
00:03:34,560 --> 00:03:36,890
Tomorrow is Miss Chen Ziqing's birthday.

55
00:03:37,160 --> 00:03:38,490
Don't forget to attend.

56
00:03:41,680 --> 00:03:42,079
Okay.

57
00:03:52,840 --> 00:03:54,700
Actually, I know their birthdays

58
00:03:54,800 --> 00:03:56,130
even better than you do.

59
00:04:14,320 --> 00:04:15,280
Pleasure doing business with you.

60
00:04:15,280 --> 00:04:15,640
Pleasure doing business with you.

61
00:04:15,640 --> 00:04:16,200
Cheers.

62
00:04:16,240 --> 00:04:16,700
Please.

63
00:04:18,399 --> 00:04:18,930
Grandpa.

64
00:04:19,040 --> 00:04:19,500
Haoran.

65
00:04:20,440 --> 00:04:21,680
You two are finally here.

66
00:04:21,680 --> 00:04:23,680
I can't entertain everyone by myself.

67
00:04:23,680 --> 00:04:24,210
Brother.

68
00:04:24,480 --> 00:04:24,880
Grandpa.

69
00:04:24,880 --> 00:04:25,600
You guys talk.

70
00:04:25,600 --> 00:04:27,320
I'll take Haoran to meet someone.

71
00:04:27,320 --> 00:04:28,080
Let's go, Haoran.

72
00:04:28,080 --> 00:04:29,740
Old Master, please excuse us.

73
00:04:34,400 --> 00:04:36,800
These are all partners of Gu Group.

74
00:04:37,320 --> 00:04:39,180
Don't tell me you don't know them.

75
00:04:41,080 --> 00:04:41,640
Meet who?

76
00:04:42,159 --> 00:04:43,820
You'll know when you see them.

77
00:04:47,480 --> 00:04:48,000
Mr. Gu.

78
00:04:48,040 --> 00:04:50,360
I heard you won a race against Mr. Ding recently.

79
00:04:50,360 --> 00:04:52,220
When will you teach me how to race?

80
00:04:52,680 --> 00:04:53,159
Haoran.

81
00:04:53,760 --> 00:04:55,200
This is our major client.

82
00:04:55,960 --> 00:04:57,490
You didn't forget, did you?

83
00:05:06,240 --> 00:05:07,240
Looking at his expression,

84
00:05:07,240 --> 00:05:08,370
I think he forgot me.

85
00:05:10,840 --> 00:05:12,080
Mr. Xia, you must be joking.

86
00:05:12,080 --> 00:05:13,340
How could I forget you?

87
00:05:13,360 --> 00:05:15,360
The Gu Group's business in Malaysia

88
00:05:15,520 --> 00:05:16,720
still relies on your support.

89
00:05:16,720 --> 00:05:17,050
Here,

90
00:05:17,080 --> 00:05:18,410
let me offer you a toast.

91
00:05:18,560 --> 00:05:18,960
Okay.

92
00:05:23,040 --> 00:05:23,520
Mr. Gu.

93
00:05:24,520 --> 00:05:25,960
You really hide your light under a bushel.

94
00:05:25,960 --> 00:05:27,290
Mr. Li, you're too kind.

95
00:05:27,320 --> 00:05:28,760
I'll be over the moon if you keep praising me.

96
00:05:28,760 --> 00:05:30,240
You should be if you deserve it.

97
00:05:30,240 --> 00:05:31,960
Keep a low profile but do great things.

98
00:05:31,960 --> 00:05:32,480
Mr. Li,

99
00:05:32,520 --> 00:05:33,560
you're too kind.

100
00:05:34,000 --> 00:05:36,330
Our company's recent FR off-road vehicle

101
00:05:36,720 --> 00:05:38,000
seems to be selling well.

102
00:05:38,000 --> 00:05:39,800
I should buy one to study it someday.

103
00:05:39,800 --> 00:05:41,200
Could I be wrong?

104
00:05:41,600 --> 00:05:42,860
Is he really Gu Haoran?

105
00:05:42,920 --> 00:05:44,880
If Mr. Gu wants to buy it, I'll definitely give a discount.

106
00:05:44,880 --> 00:05:46,120
Is there really such a good deal?

107
00:05:46,120 --> 00:05:46,600
Come,

108
00:05:46,840 --> 00:05:47,440
let me toast to you.

109
00:05:47,440 --> 00:05:47,960
Cheers.

110
00:05:58,080 --> 00:05:59,340
I'll let you guys talk.

111
00:06:00,080 --> 00:06:02,010
I'll take you to meet someone else.

112
00:06:04,120 --> 00:06:04,680
Mr. Song.

113
00:06:06,960 --> 00:06:08,020
This... this is...

114
00:06:08,360 --> 00:06:09,290
This is Song Yun.

115
00:06:09,760 --> 00:06:11,090
Mr. Song is a well-known

116
00:06:13,760 --> 00:06:16,120
tire king in the industry.

117
00:06:16,680 --> 00:06:18,880
You even had dinner with him last month.

118
00:06:33,760 --> 00:06:34,320
Luo Xin.

119
00:06:34,920 --> 00:06:37,120
It's too hard to memorize all these materials.

120
00:06:37,120 --> 00:06:37,780
Why don't we

121
00:06:38,880 --> 00:06:39,409
use this?

122
00:06:40,600 --> 00:06:42,530
You want to use it to send messages.

123
00:06:42,640 --> 00:06:43,170
Exactly.

124
00:06:43,760 --> 00:06:44,480
With this,

125
00:06:44,880 --> 00:06:46,680
I can easily handle the banquet.

126
00:06:47,400 --> 00:06:48,600
Good thing I'm smart.

127
00:06:49,800 --> 00:06:51,440
Mr. Song, you really are forgetful.

128
00:06:51,440 --> 00:06:53,370
We had dinner together last month.

129
00:06:55,280 --> 00:06:55,800
Mr. Gu,

130
00:06:56,320 --> 00:06:58,280
wasn't the one who had dinner with me last month

131
00:06:58,280 --> 00:06:59,840
the eldest young master?

132
00:07:05,200 --> 00:07:05,760
Haoran,

133
00:07:06,160 --> 00:07:07,620
you're the one who forgot.

134
00:07:08,040 --> 00:07:08,760
Last month,

135
00:07:09,040 --> 00:07:11,500
you arranged for Mr. Song and me to eat alone.

136
00:07:12,040 --> 00:07:14,370
You even asked me to buy something for you.

137
00:07:14,520 --> 00:07:17,580
Made me run all over the city and still couldn't find it.

138
00:07:18,360 --> 00:07:18,960
I...

139
00:07:19,560 --> 00:07:20,000
Mr. Gu,

140
00:07:20,160 --> 00:07:21,090
did that happen?

141
00:07:21,240 --> 00:07:22,200
Then tell me,

142
00:07:22,440 --> 00:07:23,970
what did you want to give me?

143
00:07:24,720 --> 00:07:26,250
Mr. Song, look at my memory.

144
00:07:27,240 --> 00:07:28,640
I was going to give you...

145
00:07:30,280 --> 00:07:31,920
what was it again?

146
00:07:37,840 --> 00:07:39,100
I wanted to give you...

147
00:07:41,840 --> 00:07:42,280
Oh no,

148
00:07:43,000 --> 00:07:43,930
I made a mistake.

149
00:07:46,040 --> 00:07:47,300
I wanted to give you...

150
00:07:48,080 --> 00:07:48,560
Sir,

151
00:07:49,960 --> 00:07:50,640
your phone.

152
00:07:57,120 --> 00:07:57,720
Leave now.

153
00:07:58,600 --> 00:07:59,320
Sorry, sir.

154
00:07:59,840 --> 00:08:00,320
Luo Xin,

155
00:08:00,520 --> 00:08:01,720
you're too careless.

156
00:08:02,080 --> 00:08:03,200
Take me to change clothes now.

157
00:08:03,200 --> 00:08:03,800
Okay, sir.

158
00:08:04,600 --> 00:08:05,730
Mr. Song, excuse me.

159
00:08:09,120 --> 00:08:09,960
Damn.

160
00:08:10,240 --> 00:08:11,840
I was so close to succeeding.

161
00:08:13,920 --> 00:08:14,400
Luo Xin.

162
00:08:14,480 --> 00:08:15,680
What's wrong with you?

163
00:08:15,680 --> 00:08:16,320
How could you mess this up?

164
00:08:16,320 --> 00:08:16,920
I'm sorry.

165
00:08:17,080 --> 00:08:17,940
I was careless.

166
00:08:18,040 --> 00:08:19,280
Good thing you noticed it in time,

167
00:08:19,280 --> 00:08:20,320
or Gu Haotian would have found out

168
00:08:20,320 --> 00:08:20,840
that I'm a fake.

169
00:08:20,840 --> 00:08:21,840
Don't worry, Sir.

170
00:08:21,920 --> 00:08:23,380
I'll be careful next time.

171
00:08:26,960 --> 00:08:27,960
This kind of mistake

172
00:08:27,960 --> 00:08:29,000
must never happen again.

173
00:08:29,000 --> 00:08:30,400
Isn't this an old friend?

174
00:08:31,320 --> 00:08:32,720
Why are you working here?

175
00:08:33,640 --> 00:08:36,000
Isn't this that drunkard, Young Master Lei?

176
00:08:36,000 --> 00:08:36,600
Oh no.

177
00:08:39,000 --> 00:08:39,640
Waiter,

178
00:08:40,120 --> 00:08:42,450
did you forget to wear your uniform today?

179
00:08:44,240 --> 00:08:45,640
This is a high-end venue.

180
00:08:45,960 --> 00:08:48,220
People of your status aren't allowed in.

181
00:08:50,320 --> 00:08:51,000
Sorry.

182
00:08:51,440 --> 00:08:53,040
You've got the wrong person.

183
00:08:54,320 --> 00:08:55,380
Stop playing dumb.

184
00:08:56,120 --> 00:08:58,040
You need to know your place.

185
00:08:58,840 --> 00:08:59,200
Go.

186
00:08:59,640 --> 00:09:00,500
Pour me a drink.

187
00:09:02,840 --> 00:09:03,440
Mr. Lei,

188
00:09:04,160 --> 00:09:06,680
please show some respect to our young master.

189
00:09:06,680 --> 00:09:07,600
Young master?

190
00:09:08,080 --> 00:09:08,720
Him?

191
00:09:09,200 --> 00:09:10,480
He's just a waiter.

192
00:09:12,520 --> 00:09:13,450
I'm telling you,

193
00:09:13,760 --> 00:09:15,840
if you dare to disrespect the young master again,

194
00:09:15,840 --> 00:09:17,400
Gu Group will immediately terminate

195
00:09:17,400 --> 00:09:19,460
the cooperation with the Lei family.

196
00:09:20,400 --> 00:09:21,240
A secretary.

197
00:09:21,840 --> 00:09:23,170
Who do you think you are?

198
00:09:23,480 --> 00:09:25,140
Is it your place to speak here?

199
00:09:25,600 --> 00:09:27,000
What are you trying to do?

200
00:09:27,040 --> 00:09:28,370
Do I call the shots then?

201
00:09:33,000 --> 00:09:33,660
Old Master.

202
00:09:34,880 --> 00:09:36,280
Isn't this Old Master Gu?

203
00:09:36,600 --> 00:09:37,800
What brings you here?

204
00:09:38,240 --> 00:09:39,840
You, listen to me carefully.

205
00:09:40,280 --> 00:09:41,800
He is no waiter.

206
00:09:42,280 --> 00:09:43,280
He is my grandson,

207
00:09:43,680 --> 00:09:45,120
the heir of the Gu Group,

208
00:09:45,440 --> 00:09:46,240
Gu Haoran.

209
00:09:47,360 --> 00:09:48,840
He is Mr. Gu?

210
00:09:49,840 --> 00:09:51,040
How is this possible?

211
00:09:51,560 --> 00:09:53,290
I am officially notifying you.

212
00:09:53,440 --> 00:09:54,400
From today on,

213
00:09:54,960 --> 00:09:55,960
our Gu Group

214
00:09:56,360 --> 00:09:57,720
will never cooperate with your Lei family

215
00:09:57,720 --> 00:09:58,600
ever again.

216
00:09:59,680 --> 00:10:00,400
No.

217
00:10:00,520 --> 00:10:01,320
Old Master Gu,

218
00:10:01,520 --> 00:10:02,250
you know that

219
00:10:02,560 --> 00:10:03,800
our Lei family's little business

220
00:10:03,800 --> 00:10:05,960
relies entirely on the Gu Group to survive.

221
00:10:05,960 --> 00:10:06,920
If you cut us off,

222
00:10:07,200 --> 00:10:09,530
the Lei family will be completely ruined.

223
00:10:10,960 --> 00:10:11,480
Mr. Gu.

224
00:10:12,080 --> 00:10:12,800
I was wrong.

225
00:10:13,320 --> 00:10:14,980
I was blind to your greatness.

226
00:10:15,680 --> 00:10:17,120
Please be the bigger person

227
00:10:17,120 --> 00:10:18,380
and let me off the hook.

228
00:10:18,440 --> 00:10:20,040
I will never do it again.

229
00:10:20,600 --> 00:10:22,080
We have to put on a full show.

230
00:10:22,080 --> 00:10:23,280
I need to teach him a lesson.
